title: Influence of the hard segments content on the properties of electrospun aliphatic poly(carbonate-urethane-urea)s
content:
RSC Adv., 2024, 14,15766-15775
DOI: 10.1039/D4RA01726A, Paper

Karolina Rolińska, Hadi Bakhshi, Maria Balk, Paweł Parzuchowski, Magdalena Mazurek-Budzyńska
The study investigated the impact of hard segments (HS) content on the morphology and thermomechanical properties of electrospun aliphatic poly(carbonate-urea-urethane)s (PCUUs).
